_time_high":120.9,"all_time_low":13.11,"long_business_summary":"Pace E-Commerce Ventures Limited engages in the sale of branded, customized, and personalized products for B2C and B2B customers through digital platforms in India. It offers clothing and accessories; furnishing and home decors; fabrics; occasions and gift items; travel bags, protective cases, and other accessories; stationery products and corporate essentials, including notebooks, pens, office supplies, and branded corporate gifts; and sports and outdoor active wear. The company also provides business essentials and promotional materials, which include business cards and branded merchandise; customized indoor and outdoor signages and banners; packaging solutions; and kids products, including clothing, fashion, toys, furniture, bedding, and others. In addition, it offers software development and information technology services. Its digital platforms include cotandcandy.com, homepost.in, wishrows.com, ostilos.com, zwankee.com, zwankeeglobal.com, and pacevltd.com. The company markets its products through offline channels, such as personalized catalogues, direct mails, temporary retail spaces, and trades shows. Pace E-Commerce Ventures Limited was incorporated in 2015 and is based in Ahmedabad, India."}}